subject: Soccer
organizations: United States Women's National Soccer Team
lead_paragraph: Australia withdrew from two friendly matches that were to be part of the United States women’s national team’s World Cup victory tour, but U.S. Soccer said the games would go on with Haiti as a replacement opponent.
